posts.message:
Don't Guess it, Test it!
  
Awesome web performance talk by +[Paul Lewis](https://plus.google.com/105201233571140699617), covers: network performance tips, compute (aka JavaScript), and rendering pipelines. Lots of great tips on how to measure and optimize your performance in Chrome.  
  
Definitely check out the video, but there's also a tl;dr text version if you prefer: [http://bit.ly/YnH76L](http://bit.ly/YnH76L)
